def theta(radcoord, timecoord):
    return np.e**(-radcoord) * np.cos(timecoord) #, (((np.e**(radcoordlin/2)) * ((-np.sin(radcoordlin/2)))))

def phi(radcoord, timecoord):
    return ((np.e**(radcoord/2)) * (-np.sin(radcoord/2)))#, (((np.e**(radcoord/2)) * (np.cos(timecoord/2))))

#radcoordlin

radcoord = []
timecoord = []

#def sys1(t, theta, phi)
def sysone(ic1, ic2, cyclesone, dtt):
    radcoord.append(ic1)
    timecoord.append(ic2)
    for i in range(cyclesone):
        radcoord.append(radcoord[i] + (theta(radcoord[i], timecoord[i])) * dtt)
            #radcoord[i] * dtt)# + (theta(radcoord[i],timecoord[i])) * dtt)
        timecoord.append(timecoord[i] + (phi(radcoord[i], timecoord[i])) * dtt)
    return radcoord, timecoord

def xxone(xone):
    return np.e**(1 / xone) * 2 * np.cos(xone / 2)

def xxtwo(ttime):
    return np.e**(1 / ttime) * 2 * -np.cos(2 * ttime) - np.sin(2 * ttime)

def xxthr(ttime):
    return np.e**(2 / ttime) * 2 * np.sin(ttime / 2) - np.sin(ttime / 2)

def xxfrr(ttime):
    return np.e**(2 / ttime) * 2 * np.sin(ttime / 2) - np.sin(ttime / 2)

xone = []
xtwo = []
    
def systwo (ic3, ic4, cyclestwo, dttt):
    xone.append(ic3)
    xtwo.append(ic4)
    for i in range(cyclestwo):
        xone.append(xone[i] + xxone(xone[i]) * dttt)
        xtwo.append(xtwo[i] + xxtwo(xtwo[i]) * dttt)
    return xone, xtwo

systwo(5, 5, 500, .05)

xthr = []
xfrr = []
#xlsp = []

def systhr (ic5, ic6, ic7, cyclesthree, dtttt):

    xfrr.append(ic6)
    #xlsp.append(ic7)
    for i in range (cyclesthree):
        xthr.append(xthr[i] + xxthr(xthr[i]) * dtttt)
        xfrr.append(xfrr[i] + xxfrr(xfrr[i]) * dtttt)
        #xlsp.append([i])
    return xthr, xfrr, #xlsp

bin_size = 1

for i in rad:
    mask = (np.greater(Rad, i - bin_size) & np.less(Rad, i + bin_size))
    values = FFF[mask]#**2
    intensity[index] = np.mean(values)
    index += 1

plt.plot(rad, intensity)
